{"ID":"20241011010144-626gw28","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20241011010144-626gw28","title":"精简稿","type":"doc","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010456-fjryopl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-fjryopl","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"今天写完Java上机题后我极想吐槽Java，然后趁机给Scala布道。"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-3kby1ai","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-3kby1ai","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同一个上机题目。"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-hq52x86","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-hq52x86","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Scala语言: 3272个字符"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-x9m5mbo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-x9m5mbo","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Java语言: 6245个字符"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-pyayafa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-pyayafa","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Python: 3125个字符"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-g54651s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-g54651s","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"评价：Java没有对序列操作进行抽象。你需要好几行的的代码段来执行一个数组元素加一的操作，scala一行map, filter解决。在Java里老天保佑你大于号和大于等于号别写错了，不然GG。而scala里可以直接用to和until区分，而且你也很难遇上给循环定界限的事情。"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-lqbuy5z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-lqbuy5z","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Java的设计者大概没想到这么一个问题，对于一个程序，大概率要处理很多特性相似的东西。因为如果反过来说，如果是完全不同的东西，则需要完全不同的处理思路，那就是不同的程序了。然而Java却不给序列操作进行优化。"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-uzehuwt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-uzehuwt","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Scala不需要public staic void,"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-nmtghvd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-nmtghvd","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Scala不需要for(int i = 0; i \u003c 10; i++)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-fn5j7cp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-fn5j7cp","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Scala不需要boolean isSuccess = true if something happens isSuccess=false,"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-c7ookx2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-c7ookx2","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Scala不需要StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();"}]},{"ID":"20241011010456-ouirf27","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010456-ouirf27","updated":"20241011010456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Scala的程序不短才怪"}]}]}